1
00:00:06,200 --> 00:00:08,640
Next time, let's come hang out here again.

2
00:00:08,640 --> 00:00:09,839
Sure, sounds good!

3
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:11,839
I'm so happy!

4
00:00:12,320 --> 00:00:16,920
I wanna fly, higher and higher!

5
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:18,719
I wanna fly!

6
00:00:19,199 --> 00:00:21,399
Higher and higher I'll soar!

7
00:00:21,399 --> 00:00:22,280
I'll take you flying in a bit.

8
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:14,480
Captain Li, the beef noodles are ready.

9
00:01:14,959 --> 00:01:15,920
Here, dig in.

10
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,439
Take your time.

11
00:01:17,439 --> 00:01:18,159
I've got to get back to work.

12
00:01:18,159 --> 00:01:18,879
Come on, come on.

13
00:01:46,959 --> 00:01:48,239
Nothing beats your noodles.

14
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,120
I could eat them for a lifetime.

15
00:01:50,599 --> 00:01:52,159
Is that enough? I can cook you another bowl.

16
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:52,920
I'm good, thanks.

17
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:54,400
I'm full.

18
00:01:58,560 --> 00:01:59,599
How's the kid doing?

19
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:02,000
Getting ready for surgery.

20
00:02:05,879 --> 00:02:06,760
The money?

21
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:09,840
We've got enough.

22
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:12,560
Just about.

23
00:02:12,879 --> 00:02:13,680
Pretty much there.

24
00:02:16,599 --> 00:02:17,400
That's good.

25
00:02:20,599 --> 00:02:22,639
Captain Zhao really didn't tell you anything before he left?

26
00:02:22,919 --> 00:02:24,360
I've told you so many times.

27
00:02:24,479 --> 00:02:25,120
He didn't tell me a thing.

28
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,120
He was my mentor.

29
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,960
Can you go over the details

30
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:30,680
of that day with me again?

31
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:32,199
I've already gone over it again and again.

32
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:33,240
One more time won't hurt.

33
00:02:38,039 --> 00:02:39,199
Captain Zhao, watch out!

34
00:02:41,439 --> 00:02:42,120
Captain Zhao!

35
00:02:43,879 --> 00:02:44,560
How was that?

36
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,479
Your memory really is impressive.

37
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:53,759
You've repeated it so many times, word for word.

38
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:59,159
I failed to protect Captain Zhao.

39
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,719
It's all my fault.

40
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:02,759
When Captain Zhao split you up to chase him,

41
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,759
weren't there two men following you?

42
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,840
How did you end up alone?

43
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:12,039
The arrest scene was very chaotic that day.

44
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:13,560
There were so many exits.

45
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,319
I was afraid Ma Shijiang would get away,

46
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,719
so I split off from the others.

47
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:22,919
Captain Li,

48
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:25,479
you're not suspecting me, are you?

49
00:03:25,639 --> 00:03:26,479
Of course not.

50
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:28,280
How could I?

51
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,360
But as you know,

52
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:38,639
Captain Zhao trained me himself.

53
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,080
I can't let his death

54
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,360
go unexplained.

55
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:47,919
Right?

56
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:50,960
Right.

57
00:03:56,159 --> 00:03:56,759
Hey.

58
00:03:57,319 --> 00:03:58,400
Why are you giving me so much?

59
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,360
The kid needs it.

60
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:05,879
Take the drink.

61
00:04:09,479 --> 00:04:10,240
Captain Li.

62
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,199
Thanks.

63
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,839
I'm so happy!

64
00:04:45,319 --> 00:04:46,680
I wanna fly!

65
00:04:49,759 --> 00:04:52,240
Higher and higher I'll soar!

66
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,720
I wanna fly!

67
00:05:00,199 --> 00:05:02,360
Higher and higher I'll soar!

68
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,240
I'll take you flying in a bit.

69
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,399
Boss, there's been a homicide.

70
00:05:27,399 --> 00:05:27,920
Got it.

71
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,319
Boss, you got here fast.

72
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,399
Who called it in?

73
00:05:48,199 --> 00:05:48,920
A couple.

74
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,319
Captain Wang's questioning them now.

75
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,240
The victim is Shen Qing.

76
00:05:57,959 --> 00:05:58,759
Shen Qing?

77
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:01,720
The bank guard is our eyewitness.

78
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:02,839
But he passed out from the shock.

79
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,120
What about the medical examiner?

80
00:06:04,639 --> 00:06:05,319
On the way.

81
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:10,839
You're improving.

82
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,040
Of course I am.

83
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:37,680
Li Kaiyang.

84
00:07:38,759 --> 00:07:40,319
Are you addicted to playing ME?

85
00:07:43,959 --> 00:07:44,959
I'm warning you.

86
00:07:45,399 --> 00:07:46,439
Don't contaminate the scene.

87
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,439
Did you hear me?

88
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:54,319
Like it or not, I'm your superior now.

89
00:07:54,959 --> 00:07:57,079
Can you show some respect for authority?

90
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:58,519
I'm leading this case.

91
00:07:59,079 --> 00:07:59,759
You're assisting.

92
00:08:00,199 --> 00:08:01,800
Captain Zhao spoiled you too much.

93
00:08:04,079 --> 00:08:05,600
Did you just bring up my mentor?

94
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:06,480
What about it?

95
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,199
However my mentor handled cases,

96
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:09,439
that's how I'll handle them now.

97
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:10,120
Got a problem with that?

98
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:11,560
No one's stopping you from investigating.

99
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:13,040
Hey, Boss, Boss, Boss.

100
00:08:13,199 --> 00:08:14,399
Captain Wang's just focused on the case.

101
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,360
Captain Zhao gave his life.

102
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,360
We're all grieving.

103
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:19,399
But you can't keep using that as an excuse.

104
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:23,959
A word of advice:

105
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:26,839
Be careful how you use your captain's authority.

106
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,680
I don't need your reminder.

107
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,399
Jiang Han.

108
00:08:30,959 --> 00:08:32,799
Captain Wang, that's just how my boss is.

109
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:34,120
With homicides, he doesn't hold back.

110
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:36,000
Enough, you've only been here a few days.

111
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:37,279
I know him better than you do.

112
00:08:37,279 --> 00:08:38,279
I'll... I'll get going.

113
00:08:38,639 --> 00:08:39,320
Boss!

114
00:09:49,559 --> 00:09:50,879
If Shen Qing

115
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:54,759
fell backward while sitting on the rooftop edge,

116
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:57,879
the position of her body

117
00:09:57,879 --> 00:10:00,120
wouldn't match what we saw at the scene.

118
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:13,159
And if she was standing on the rooftop

119
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:16,720
and fell forward,

120
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,879
the position of her body

121
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:26,039
still wouldn't match the scene.

122
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:37,320
So what have you figured out?

123
00:10:39,399 --> 00:10:40,799
I mean, she came up here alone,

124
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:44,320
late at night in her pajamas, to drink on the roof.

125
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:46,080
How devastated must she have been?

126
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,559
If it was suicide,

127
00:10:47,559 --> 00:10:49,480
why come all the way to the bank's rooftop?

128
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:50,919
And if it was murder,

129
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,720
someone must have lured her here.

130
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,039
But...

131
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:56,080
that doesn't make sense either.

132
00:10:57,159 --> 00:10:58,000
Right, Boss?

133
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,399
Boss?

134
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,399
Boss?

135
00:11:05,759 --> 00:11:06,480
Boss?

136
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:09,320
Boss?

137
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,519
Boss?

138
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,399
Boss?

139
00:11:13,399 --> 00:11:14,360
Stop yelling.

140
00:11:16,559 --> 00:11:18,159
Boss, you scared me to death!

141
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,879
This is a good hiding spot.

142
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:22,000
Don't ever tell me you're brave again.

143
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:25,120
Even the bravest can't take a scare like that!

144
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:26,519
Pass the word.

145
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:27,639
Seal this place off.

146
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:29,159
No unauthorized personnel allowed in.

147
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,720
Was Shen Qing a bank executive?

148
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:43,720
Yes.

149
00:11:44,519 --> 00:11:46,799
She was the director of our credit department.

150
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,879
Who is it, this late at night?

151
00:11:52,559 --> 00:11:53,440
Old Li, it's me.

152
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,480
Open up, hurry!

153
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,440
Oh, it's Director Shen.

154
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,720
It's so late. Is something wrong?

155
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,159
I... well...

156
00:11:59,159 --> 00:12:00,759
I left something in my office.

157
00:12:00,759 --> 00:12:01,679
I'm just going to grab it.

158
00:12:01,879 --> 00:12:02,600
It's pretty dark in there.

159
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:03,360
Let me go with you.

160
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:03,799
No need, no need.

161
00:12:03,799 --> 00:12:05,039
Just stay at your post.

162
00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:05,919
Director, be careful!

163
00:12:05,919 --> 00:12:06,559
Okay.

164
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:13,000
She headed up to the rooftop after she went in.

165
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:14,240
Ah.

166
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,600
I really didn't notice.

167
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:18,159
How long after she went in did the power go out?

168
00:12:19,399 --> 00:12:20,320
At most...

169
00:12:21,159 --> 00:12:22,600
five or six minutes at most.

170
00:12:52,559 --> 00:12:54,679
Oh no, I left the keys on the desk.

171
00:12:55,279 --> 00:12:56,559
Getting old, I guess.

172
00:12:57,399 --> 00:12:58,559
Well, I'll have to go back for them.

173
00:13:12,519 --> 00:13:13,360
Director Shen?

174
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:31,919
Oh my god!

175
00:13:32,519 --> 00:13:33,679
That really scared me to death!

176
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,320
Scared me to death.

177
00:13:35,799 --> 00:13:36,639
Catch your breath first.

178
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:40,200
Did you hear anyone walking in the fire escape?

179
00:13:41,399 --> 00:13:42,039
Well...

180
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,320
I can't be sure.

181
00:13:44,159 --> 00:13:45,360
The bank's back courtyard

182
00:13:45,879 --> 00:13:47,480
has several stray cats.

183
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,320
At night,

184
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:51,519
they make noise catching mice too.

185
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,200
The woman who fell is Shen Qing.

186
00:13:55,799 --> 00:13:58,799
28, Credit Director at Fengdu Bank.

187
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:02,440
Time of death: yesterday at 22:55.

188
00:14:02,879 --> 00:14:05,159
Location: Fengdu Bank office building.

189
00:14:05,759 --> 00:14:07,000
Suicide or homicide?

190
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:08,240
Any preliminary conclusions?

191
00:14:08,399 --> 00:14:09,039
Not yet.

192
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:12,360
We need the forensic and trace evidence reports first

193
00:14:12,639 --> 00:14:13,879
before launching a deeper investigation.

194
00:14:15,679 --> 00:14:16,360
Chief Xing.

195
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,279
Found any leads yet?

196
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,279
Not so far.

197
00:14:20,799 --> 00:14:22,039
But once the bank opens,

198
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:23,440
I'd like to meet their president.

199
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:25,480
No need to wait.

200
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,639
I'll have someone notify him right away

201
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:29,879
and have him cooperate with the investigation at the bank.

202
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:33,440
The damaging impact of this case

203
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:36,000
will spread very quickly.

204
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:37,960
Whether it's suicide or homicide,

205
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,639
set up a task force immediately

206
00:14:39,919 --> 00:14:41,279
and conduct a thorough investigation.

207
00:14:41,919 --> 00:14:42,519
Yes, sir.

208
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,759
Wang Yonglin will lead the task force,

209
00:14:45,039 --> 00:14:46,200
Li Kaiyang as deputy.

210
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:47,840
Oh, by the way,

211
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:50,960
About next week's provincial CID captain training,

212
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:51,759
who's going?

213
00:14:52,279 --> 00:14:53,759
Let Li Kaiyang go.

214
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:56,159
He's young, with more room to grow than me.

215
00:14:56,679 --> 00:14:58,440
The provincial training is for CID captains.

216
00:14:59,039 --> 00:14:59,879
I'm only a deputy captain.

217
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,440
Captain Wang should be the one going.

218
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,320
That frees me up to work the case.

219
00:15:04,519 --> 00:15:05,320
Li Kaiyang.

220
00:15:05,960 --> 00:15:07,559
Why the hostility?

221
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:10,159
Am I holding up your investigation here?

222
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:11,799
You can take it that way if you want.

223
00:15:11,799 --> 00:15:12,399
Enough.

224
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:14,120
In front of Chief Gao,

225
00:15:14,759 --> 00:15:16,000
look at what you two are doing.

226
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:16,960
Seriously?

227
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:21,360
Lao Wang, don't mind me saying this,

228
00:15:21,679 --> 00:15:22,840
You're a captain now.

229
00:15:24,159 --> 00:15:26,440
Time to rein in that temper of yours.

230
00:15:27,039 --> 00:15:28,840
Speak with the big picture in mind.

231
00:15:29,159 --> 00:15:30,039
That's enough, Lao Xing.

232
00:15:30,759 --> 00:15:31,480
Li Kaiyang,

233
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:34,480
You'll head the task force.

234
00:15:35,159 --> 00:15:37,720
I hope you crack this case as soon as possible.

235
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:39,320
Thank you, Chief Gao.

236
00:15:43,519 --> 00:15:44,480
Then you go, fine.

237
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:49,639
Hey.

238
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:51,360
How did this dog get in here again?

239
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:52,360
Out.

240
00:15:53,039 --> 00:15:53,919
Out you go, hey.

241
00:16:07,519 --> 00:16:08,440
Captain Li, I presume?

242
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:11,559
Hello.

243
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:12,679
Hello.

244
00:16:12,679 --> 00:16:13,200
An honor to meet you.

245
00:16:13,759 --> 00:16:15,360
I'm Su Zhuang, the bank president.

246
00:16:15,639 --> 00:16:16,399
Li Kaiyang.

247
00:16:16,639 --> 00:16:17,960
My colleague, Jiang Han.

248
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:21,200
Calling you out before dawn,

249
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:22,720
sorry to bother you.

250
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:23,360
Oh, please.

251
00:16:23,639 --> 00:16:24,559
A life is at stake.

252
00:16:24,879 --> 00:16:25,919
I wouldn't dare delay.

253
00:16:26,279 --> 00:16:27,120
Let's talk in the office.

254
00:16:27,879 --> 00:16:28,919
We'll re-examine the scene first.

255
00:16:29,759 --> 00:16:31,759
Alright, I'll wait in the office.
